      "x": 535,
      "y": 813,
      "width": 216,
      "height": 231,
      "text": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: tan30° = 50/d\nStep 2: 1/√3 = 50/d → d = 50√3\n  = 86.6 m\n\nTRICK:\n30° → d = h×√3\n60° → d = h/√3\n45° → d = h\n\n         T\n   50m   |\\ 30°\n         |____\\\n        B d=?  O\n\nAnswer: 86.6 m ✓",
