    {
      "id": "el_36",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1005,
      "y": 813,
      "width": 202,
      "height": 274,
      "text": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: d₁=h/√3, d₂=h√3\n  d₂-d₁ = 40\nStep 2: h√3-h/√3 = 40\n  2h/√3 = 40 → h = 20√3\n\nTRICK:\nh = d×tanα×tanβ/(tanα-tanβ)\n= 40×√3×(1/√3)/(√3-1/√3)\n= 40×1/(2/√3) = 20√3 = 34.64\n\n       T\n  h=?  |\\  60°\n       | \\______P (closer)\n       |  \\  30°\n       |___\\____Q (farther)\n       B  d1  40m\n\nAnswer: 34.64 m ✓",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 12,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "seed": 3600,
