      ],
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: d₁=h/√3, d₂=h√3\n  d₂-d₁ = 40\nStep 2: h√3-h/√3 = 40\n  2h/√3 = 40 → h = 20√3\n\nTRICK:\nh = d×tanα×tanβ/(tanα-tanβ)\n= 40×√3×(1/√3)/(√3-1/√3)\n= 40×1/(2/√3) = 20√3 = 34.64\n\n       T\n  h=?  |\\  60°\n       | \\______P (closer)\n       |  \\  30°\n       |___\\____Q (farther)\n       B  d1  40m\n\nAnswer: 34.64 m ✓",
