    {
      "id": "el_41",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 65,
      "y": 1253,
      "width": 267,
      "height": 274,
      "text": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: tan30°=20/d → d=20√3\nStep 2: tan60°=(20+t)/d\n  √3=(20+t)/20√3\n  60=20+t → t=40\n\nTRICK:\nTotal/Hill = tanα/tanβ\n= tan60°/tan30° = √3/(1/√3) = 3\nTotal = 3×20 = 60, Tower = 60-20 = 40\n\n       T  ← tower top\n  t=?  |     60°\n       H  ← hill top ──\n  20m  |     30°       |\n       B──────────────O\n       base     d=20√3\n\nAnswer: Tower = 40 m ✓",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 12,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "seed": 4100,
