    {
      "id": "el_46",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 535,
      "y": 1253,
      "width": 245,
      "height": 245,
      "text": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: Height diff = 30-20 = 10m\nStep 2: tan30° = 10/d\n  1/√3 = 10/d → d = 10√3\n\nTRICK:\nDraw horizontal from shorter top\nUse height DIFFERENCE only\nd = diff/tan(angle) = 10√3 = 17.32\n\n  T2(30)          T1(20)\n   |  10m diff     |\n   |──── 30° ──────| ← horizontal\n   |               |\n   └───── d=? ─────┘\n\nAnswer: 17.32 m ✓",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
