    {
      "id": "el_51",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1005,
      "y": 1253,
      "width": 238,
      "height": 173,
      "text": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: tan45°=h/12 → h=12m\nStep 2: tan60°=12/s → s=12/√3\n  = 4√3 = 6.93m\n\nTRICK:\nAt 45°: shadow = height (always!)\nSo h=12, then at 60°: s=h/√3\n= 12/√3 = 4√3\nSun rises → shadow shrinks\n\nAnswer: 6.93 m ✓",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 12,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
