      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: tan45°=h/12 → h=12m\nStep 2: tan60°=12/s → s=12/√3\n  = 4√3 = 6.93m\n\nTRICK:\nAt 45°: shadow = height (always!)\nSo h=12, then at 60°: s=h/√3\n= 12/√3 = 4√3\nSun rises → shadow shrinks\n\nAnswer: 6.93 m ✓",
