      "x": 535,
      "y": 1693,
      "width": 195,
      "height": 274,
      "text": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: d1=100√3 (at 30°)\n  d2=100/√3 (at 60°)\nStep 2: dist = d1-d2\n  = 100√3-100/√3 = 200/√3\n\nTRICK:\nDist = h(cotα - cotβ)\n= 100(√3 - 1/√3) = 100×2/√3\n= 200√3/3 = 115.47\n\n          Man\n  100m    |\\  30°     60°\n          | \\─────────/\n          |__\\_______/\n         B  d2  car  d1\n         car moves d1-d2\n\nAnswer: 115.47 m ✓",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 12,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
