      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: d1=100√3 (at 30°)\n  d2=100/√3 (at 60°)\nStep 2: dist = d1-d2\n  = 100√3-100/√3 = 200/√3\n\nTRICK:\nDist = h(cotα - cotβ)\n= 100(√3 - 1/√3) = 100×2/√3\n= 200√3/3 = 115.47\n\n          Man\n  100m    |\\  30°     60°\n          | \\─────────/\n          |__\\_______/\n         B  d2  car  d1\n         car moves d1-d2\n\nAnswer: 115.47 m ✓",
