    {
      "id": "el_66",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1005,
      "y": 1693,
      "width": 238,
      "height": 173,
      "text": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: Ladder = hypotenuse = 10m\n  sin60°=h/10 → h=5√3=8.66\nStep 2: cos60°=d/10 → d=5\n\nTRICK:\nLadder problems: use sin & cos\nsin = height/ladder\ncos = foot-dist/ladder\nVerify: (5√3)²+5²=75+25=100=10² ✓\n\nAnswer: h=8.66m, d=5m ✓",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 12,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "seed": 6600,
