    {
      "id": "el_76",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 535,
      "y": 2133,
      "width": 260,
      "height": 288,
      "text": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: String = hypotenuse\n  sin60° = 75/L\nStep 2: √3/2 = 75/L → L = 150/√3\n  = 50√3 = 86.6\n\nTRICK:\nString/Ladder = hypotenuse → use sin\nL = height/sin(angle)\n= 75/sin60° = 75×2/√3 = 50√3\n\n      Kite\n       /|\n   L  / | 75m\n     /  |\n    /60°|\n   /____|\n   ground\n\nAnswer: 86.6 m ✓",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 12,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
