      "originalText": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: String = hypotenuse\n  sin60° = 75/L\nStep 2: √3/2 = 75/L → L = 150/√3\n  = 50√3 = 86.6\n\nTRICK:\nString/Ladder = hypotenuse → use sin\nL = height/sin(angle)\n= 75/sin60° = 75×2/√3 = 50√3\n\n      Kite\n       /|\n   L  / | 75m\n     /  |\n    /60°|\n   /____|\n   ground\n\nAnswer: 86.6 m ✓",
